---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Chiron"
  description="Learn about Chiron and our mission to help athletes and fitness enthusiasts achieve their training goals."
>
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8 text-center">
        About Chiron
      </h1>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg prose-primary max-w-none">
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 text-center">
          Inspired by the wise centaur of Greek mythology, Chiron, we strive to help coaches and self-coached athletes shape their destinies and perform at their best. Like legendary heroes such as Achilles, Atalanta, Heracles, Jason, and Theseus who were guided by Chiron, our mission is to empower coaches and athletes on their journey to peak performance.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            We believe that everyone has the potential to achieve their athletic goals. Our mission is to provide expert guidance, science-backed training methods, and actionable advice to help you train smarter and perform better.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">What We Offer</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-600">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span><strong>Training Articles:</strong> In-depth guides on training methodologies, periodization, and performance optimization.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span><strong>Blog Posts:</strong> Regular updates on fitness trends, athlete stories, and practical tips.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span><strong>Newsletter:</strong> Weekly curated content delivered straight to your inbox.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Meet the Founder</h2>
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center md:items-start gap-6">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <img 
                src="/images/founder-placeholder.svg" 
                alt="Clive Gross - Founder of Chiron" 
                class="w-48 h-48 rounded-full object-cover bg-gray-200"
              />
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Clive Gross</h3>
              <p class="text-primary-600 font-medium mb-4">Founder</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                Clive is a professional engineer, family man and obsessive amateur distance runner based in Brisbane, Australia. Outside of his day job, Clive combines his passion for endurance sport, exercise physiology, technology and data science into the Chiron project.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
